<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Heart_of_Glass_(song)&action=edit&section=7.php.html" title="Edit section: Remixes and samplings">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Remixes_and_samplings">Remixes and samplings</span></h2>
<table class="metadata mbox-small" style="border:1px solid #aaa; background-color:#f9f9f9;">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
