<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Heart_of_Glass_(song)&action=edit&section=9.php.html" title="Edit section: Sales and certifications">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sales_and_certifications">Sales and certifications</span></h3>
